{"tid":1232341,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"唔好再衝住 呢一刻見好就收","createTime":"2019-06-16T15:11:45.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-16T16:05:22.000Z","uid":260538,"like":88,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"31923011a20638e05f08662cbd8bbac3a4950c3f","tid":1232341,"uid":260538,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T15:11:45.000Z","msg":"大家唔好衝 就算留守都係唱下聖詩就算<br />\n千祈唔好比狗挑釁或者挑釁d狗 唔好起衝突<br />\n呢一刻衝無乜意思 唔好送頭<br />\n一黎大家行左成日都體力無乜<br />\n二黎入黑之後無哂人可以幫到手 無back up無support<br />\n三黎入黑無乜記者照住 一郁手就一定輸<br />\n同埋呢一刻道理係我地呢邊 要比時間對方回應 一郁手輿論就會大轉向 <br />\n唔好送頭 唔好令果位兄弟既犧牲白廢<br />\n同埋再衝突既話就無乜可能利用輿論要求推翻暴動定性 好難令佢地放番而家比人拉左果班兄弟<br />\n暫時見好就收 睇下有咩回覆再諗下下一步著<br />\n唔好衝突 忍住挑釁啊咁多位"},{"pid":"a2758239c40e182dfef4a508fc218d345906059b","tid":1232341,"uid":260370,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T15:12:35.000Z","msg":"pish<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"92f50e9e771a7b4aafacfaea96fcca55587d51e8","tid":1232341,"uid":260538,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T15:13:33.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"0086eea2b5be7799df8734686d2e74f040b015ee","tid":1232341,"uid":34409,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T15:13:46.000Z","msg":"agree，其實可以諗諗留力到烈士頭七"},{"pid":"477a46204510ee171252b4a1b620b2dff4d73be1","tid":1232341,"uid":33437,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T15:15:03.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"1fd6c8c120b61c6d4ed77ee71646945c79b8bf51","tid":1232341,"uid":8512,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T15:15:18.000Z","msg":"同意，留力，要中時機"},{"pid":"cce9dcc7b9274ff1dd5add9d1f52e39ae1143693","tid":1232341,"uid":260538,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T15:17:24.000Z","msg":"記住唔好衝動啊兄弟們"},{"pid":"8f7e2323d009697ac666b55d4054f5c0c1175d96","tid":1232341,"uid":36592,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T15:18:00.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"859728d8c